---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<Layout
  title="About | AI Collective Hampton Roads"
  description="The AI Collective Hampton Roads is the local chapter of a 210,000-member global community — making AI education accessible to everyone in the 757 through free events, workshops, and neighbor-to-neighbor learning."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">About the Chapter</span>
      <h1 class="display">A community space for learning AI together in Hampton Roads.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose">
        <span class="section-number">01 — Who We Are</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Your local chapter of a global community.</h2>
        <p>The AI Collective Hampton Roads is the 757 chapter of The AI Collective, a global community of 210,000+ members exploring AI together. We're volunteer-led, community-supported, and open to anyone curious about AI — students, career changers, small-business owners, engineers, educators, retirees, and everyone in between.</p>
        <p>Our chapter runs free public events across the region, hands-on workshops for learners at every level, and private sessions for organizations that want to bring us in. In 2025 we welcomed over 1,000 neighbors to 49 gatherings. In 2026 we're planning 70+.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section team-section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-number">02 — Meet the Team</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">The operators behind the sessions.</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Our core facilitators bring decades of combined experience building, shipping, and teaching AI across enterprise, government, and startup environments.</p>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card">
          <img src={`${base}/photos/Andrewspeaker.png`} alt="Andrew Stafford" class="team-photo" loading="lazy" />
          <h3 class="team-name">Andrew Stafford</h3>
          <div class="team-role">Co-Lead, AIC Hampton Roads</div>
          <p class="team-bio">Keynote speaker and workshop facilitator focused on practical AI adoption for small and mid-sized businesses. Lead architect behind the chapter's workshop curriculum.</p>
          <a href="mailto:andrewstafford@aicollective.com" class="team-link">andrewstafford@aicollective.com &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <img src={`${base}/photos/Tedspeaker.jpg`} alt="Ted Patterson" class="team-photo" loading="lazy" />
          <h3 class="team-name">Ted Patterson</h3>
          <div class="team-role">Co-Lead, AIC Hampton Roads</div>
          <p class="team-bio">Mid-Atlantic regional director and author. Delivers keynotes, leads 1-on-1 mentorship sessions at Assembly, and runs executive workshops on AI-first business strategy.</p>
          <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/757-1on1-assistance/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="team-link">Book a 1-on-1 Mentorship Session &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <img src={`${base}/photos/Erinspeaker.png`} alt="Erin" class="team-photo" loading="lazy" />
          <h3 class="team-name">Erin</h3>
          <div class="team-role">Facilitator & Community Lead</div>
          <p class="team-bio">Workshop facilitator specializing in Vibecoding, web creation, and hands-on AI tooling sessions. Built and maintains the chapter's community platforms.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-number">03 — How the Chapter Works</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">A few things we believe.</h2>
      <div class="apart-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Everyone's Welcome</h3>
          <p>No AI background required. Our events bring together complete beginners and seasoned practitioners — because everyone learns faster when the room is mixed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Learning from Practitioners</h3>
          <p>Our facilitators and guest speakers are people who build and use AI in the real world. Less theory, more stories, real tools, and honest takes on what works.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Free Where We Can</h3>
          <p>Community meetups, demo nights, and most workshops are free. When organizations bring us in privately, those fees fund the chapter's community programming.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Rooted in the 757</h3>
          <p>We meet at places our neighbors already go — ODU, Norfolk State, ECPI, Assembly, The Hive, local businesses. Part of a global community, based here at home.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="band-teal section testimonial-band">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">What Attendees Say</span>
      <blockquote class="pull-quote display">
        "Great insight into Claude, integrations, and the orchestration of tasks you can set up. Awesome."
      </blockquote>
      <div class="quote-attrib">— Kiran · Claude Code: From Setup to Agentic Workflows · ★★★★★</div>
      <div class="quote-meta">Independent 5-star review · one of 129 ratings averaging 4.7/5 across our 2025 sessions</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-number">04 — The Parent Org</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Backed by The AI Collective.</h2>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>The AI Collective is a 210,000+ member global nonprofit dedicated to making AI education accessible and actionable. With chapters in major technology hubs worldwide, the organization connects practitioners, researchers, and business leaders to advance responsible AI adoption. AI Collective Hampton Roads is the local chapter serving the greater Hampton Roads region.</p>
        <a href="https://www.aicollective.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-md);">Visit The AI Collective &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-number">05 — Who We Work With</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">From executives to emerging talent.</h2>
      <div class="table-wrapper">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Audience</th>
              <th>Examples</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Executive Leadership</strong></td>
              <td>CEO, CTO, CPO, CFO, Directors, Business Owners</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Technical & Product</strong></td>
              <td>Engineers, AI Researchers, Product Managers</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Creative & Marketing</strong></td>
              <td>UX/UI Designers, Content Creators, Writers, Social Media Teams</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Operations & Strategy</strong></td>
              <td>Project Managers, AI Consultants, Policy Specialists</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Emerging Talent</strong></td>
              <td>University students from ODU, NSU, CNU, ECPI</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    max-width: 860px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }

  .section-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .testimonial-band {
    padding: calc(var(--spacing-2xl) * 0.8) 0;
  }

  .pull-quote {
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--color-white);
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  }

  .quote-attrib {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .quote-meta {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .prose {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .prose p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .apart-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .team-section .section-subtitle {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .team-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .team-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .team-photo {
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-md);
    display: block;
    border: 4px solid var(--color-bg-alt);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .team-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .team-role {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .team-bio {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .team-link {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    display: inline-block;
    word-break: break-word;
  }

  .table-wrapper {
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .apart-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .team-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .team-photo {
      width: 130px;
      height: 130px;
    }
  }
</style>
